data.description:
Welcome Home to Windstone! You will love this 4 Bedroom 3 Bath Home. Front Porch overlooks the community area with walking trail & pond. Kitchen has Island Snack Bar, Granite, Stainless Appliances, Smooth Cook Top, Custom Cabinets, Pantry, Breakfast Area & Separate Dining Room. 
Living Room has Built In a bookshelves on both sides of Fireplace. Hardwood throughout the main living area, Crown Molding through out living space,  2 Bedrooms, 2 baths downstairs & 2 Bedrooms 1 bath upstairs. 
Primary Bedroom has large Salon Bath with separate Shower & Tub, Granite. Large floored Walk In Attic. Laundry Room. Tankless Water Heater. Built in Office space. Covered Patio.
Privacy Fence. Double Garage. Make an Appointment today and Lets Get Movin!
